metadata.description:
CHARACTERS #2

EASY COME AND EASY GO

lyrics.text:
You told me
What you want
What you seek
I wish I
Had known
What you need

Wasted
All of my time on you
Bet you feel the same
Faking
Tellin me lies aren't you
I would do the same too

I tried my best
To come around for you
To hold it down for you
My fingers crossed
You'll come back for me
Eventually

Easy come and easy go
Maybe I should let it go
Maybe I should let you fly
Or I'll keep you by my side

I was reaching for the door
If only I had a key
If only I had a dream
Without you in it, wishful thinking

You told me
What you want
What you seek
I wish I
Had known
What you need

metadata.name: WISHFUL THINKING! #1
metadata.title: WISHFUL THINKING!
